Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.36,0:01:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.08,0:01:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷恩·塞克斯果然是很难搞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.70,0:01:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们能够出席Greatful Sound吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.92,0:01:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之他说回去考虑一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.21,0:01:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考虑…吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.30,0:02:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我借你去找他的旅费
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.97,0:02:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个月可以还清吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.89,0:02:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是会为了钱就雇杀手刺杀艾莉卡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.52,0:02:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  跟他对上可是有多少条命也不够啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.06,0:02:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.40,0:02:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快把旅费还我喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.74,0:02:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.78,0:02:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会忽然被杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.58,0:02:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Write Music」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.41,0:02:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要还喔  旅费
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.79,0:02:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些都是弘美买的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只是在旧书店买的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这样就能多学上几首曲子了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.30,0:02:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有干劲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.80,0:02:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有吉他却不会弹也太逊了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.18,0:02:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这些书很难懂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.42,0:02:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是别太相信书上的为好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.23,0:02:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也有很多出错的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.94,0:03:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我要怎么学曲子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.57,0:03:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用耳朵把听到的曲子直接复制过来比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.87,0:03:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然人各有不同
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.95,0:03:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我为例的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先去买一本和弦书
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.98,0:03:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之是先不断练习和弦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.04,0:03:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是说那种有画着手指该按的地方的书吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.05,0:03:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是压下去再弹就会出现合音的那种
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.76,0:03:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当时就是尽量多记几种和弦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.72,0:03:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话就可以靠听力来记住曲子了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.10,0:03:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后还要向周围的人请教一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.65,0:03:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.90,0:03:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雄果然是天才
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.98,0:03:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.44,0:03:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是很普通的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.90,0:03:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我觉得小雄的听力真的很敏锐喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.82,0:03:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之就是要一步一步稳扎稳打
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.58,0:03:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是怎样的天才也不可能一下子就变厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,0:03:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我既没有别的长处
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.13,0:03:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弹吉他也让我很快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.84,0:04:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从来没有一次会觉得痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.97,0:04:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许是有那么一次吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.55,0:04:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有了露西露的龙介
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.74,0:04:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就改用了Les Paul Custom
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音色果然是无法与露西露相比
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.74,0:04:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙介对此非常不满
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.25,0:04:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是龙介创作出来的曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.33,0:04:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上大家的混音完成的Brain Stone
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.46,0:04:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这首曲子是目前为止最具攻击性的杰作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.60,0:04:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋天时我们再出一张新专辑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.53,0:04:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙介
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在完全没有新曲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.36,0:05:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么呀  难道要出翻唱专辑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.00,0:05:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  要创作新曲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.40,0:05:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一张专辑打入了美国地下音乐排行的前十名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.78,0:05:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们却一毛钱也没分到  很不甘心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.91,0:05:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还不都怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  来做专辑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.59,0:05:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先别说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.67,0:05:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Greatful Sound那边到底是怎么回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.80,0:05:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷恩还没有联络我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.34,0:05:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷恩那家伙真的可靠吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.68,0:05:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有其他办法了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多多捧场…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是BECK  请多多捧场
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.74,0:05:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫BECK
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.03,0:05:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们就想不到别的名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.21,0:05:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都在想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:06:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样真的会有效果吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.25,0:06:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实这些费用也不少的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.54,0:06:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  像这种宣传方式最重要的就是耐性
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有一个人看到传单觉得很有趣而来看我们的Live
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.35,0:06:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就有可能把我们宣传开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.11,0:06:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多多捧场
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.35,0:06:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是BECK
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.44,0:06:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有兴趣请来看看我们的Live
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.15,0:06:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.71,0:06:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们就是今天的对手乐团吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.00,0:06:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫做BECK  真是不知所谓的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.92,0:06:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在杂志上看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.38,0:06:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个戴帽子的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.84,0:06:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在DB的电影里闪过了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.22,0:06:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说上次在Whisky a Go Go的演出造成很大的轰动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.97,0:07:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过八成只是些肤浅的二流乐团罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.52,0:07:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在Marquee里存活下去可是很困难的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.86,0:07:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正他们是逃不过被淘汰的命运的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.43,0:07:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来要被淘汰的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.50,0:07:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许是我们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.40,0:07:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店长  你觉得BECK怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.19,0:07:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我的Live House还不能结束啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:07:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有去涉谷看了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.44,0:08:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉人好帅喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.91,0:08:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的被电到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（吉人制造涉谷混乱）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.71,0:08:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为宣传这是最好的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.01,0:08:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Greatful Sound的入门票好象也卖得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.34,0:08:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涉谷混乱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.01,0:08:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是在模仿Stones当年在纽约的宣传吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.81,0:08:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stones吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.27,0:08:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我们比起来真是天壤之别呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.19,0:08:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人各有不同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.44,0:08:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有我们的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.22,0:08:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙介
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.99,0:08:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小雄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.24,0:08:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在正要去钓鱼池那里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件东西想要托你交给真帆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.87,0:08:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她现在就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.72,0:08:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.13,0:08:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 给 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.59,0:08:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我妈妈给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.94,0:08:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.09,0:09:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是酸梅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.14,0:09:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她看见真帆吃得很起劲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.73,0:09:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.02,0:09:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.27,0:09:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的同学Melanie
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am fine thank you how are you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.55,0:09:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人要问候小雄喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.03,0:09:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很有趣喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.70,0:09:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日语…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看她这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.78,0:09:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Melanie可是在日本出生的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.66,0:09:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日语也说得很流利  所以不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.16,0:09:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真帆前一阵子住你家了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.87,0:09:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙很会磨牙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.17,0:09:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.74,0:09:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙磨牙磨得厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.13,0:09:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前吉人也曾说过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.42,0:09:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.67,0:09:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛要说这些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.55,0:09:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.94,0:09:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于真帆来说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.50,0:09:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住朋友家并不稀奇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.40,0:09:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会心跳加速的就只有我一个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.41,0:10:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美国真不愧是先进国家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.83,0:10:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  千叶要演出吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.54,0:10:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说在10点左右出场
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.63,0:10:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说只要跟接待的说出他的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.71,0:10:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能免费进场了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.43,0:10:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千叶那家伙到底在搞些什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.56,0:10:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙还真拼命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:10:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道千叶他想退出BECK
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.96,0:10:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而认真做这边的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.59,0:11:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是他的独门修炼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.09,0:11:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他对于没跟我们做同一个梦一直都很耿耿于怀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.68,0:11:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千叶把Mongolian Chop Squard看成是自己生命的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.85,0:11:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是这种男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.40,0:11:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.15,0:11:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们怎么可能为了一个梦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.61,0:11:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就抛弃我们的招牌主唱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.74,0:11:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.63,0:11:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.20,0:11:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.44,0:11:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,30)}白痴…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.95,0:12:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.41,0:12:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的羽毛被剪过了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.66,0:12:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该不会飞远才对的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.37,0:12:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斋藤先生什么时候出差回来？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雄很喜欢斋藤先生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.13,0:12:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.17,0:12:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好歹他也是我的吉他师傅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.55,0:12:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前吃早餐的时候你妈妈说了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.62,0:12:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.39,0:12:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸雄小时候就是个奇怪的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.27,0:12:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很担心他的将来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.44,0:12:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈她… 偶尔会说这些话题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.01,0:12:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我完全不记得小时候的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.49,0:12:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以没什么实感
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.78,0:12:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会爬上书桌唱歌  你还真奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.41,0:12:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在只是个平凡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且胆小怕事的年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.55,0:13:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我要走咯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.26,0:13:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酸梅的道谢要好好代我向你妈妈说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.43,0:13:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不来我家了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我赶尾班车回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.27,0:13:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为跟小雄两人在一起  我会紧张得睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送你到车站
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.59,0:13:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.96,0:13:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不觉得小雄是个平凡人喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.34,0:13:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.01,0:13:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能早日找到贝吉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.04,0:13:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见咯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.96,0:13:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.81,0:13:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见  小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.61,0:14:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我… 为了能好好生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.04,0:14:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不知不觉间变得随波逐流起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.71,0:14:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾迪好像说过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.00,0:14:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在意别人眼光而活的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.46,0:14:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的人生不是自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.84,0:14:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认真地思考生与死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.84,0:14:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不正常啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.52,0:14:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的我说不定也还是个怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.34,0:16:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝吉跟着唱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.32,0:16:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就证明你的曲子厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.41,0:16:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是也不知道会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.07,0:16:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有几个小节而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果它不在的话也许就能完成
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.02,0:16:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓到贝吉之后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.79,0:16:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵感就全没了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.34,0:16:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浮出来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.05,0:16:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在想起来那感觉还真奇妙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.84,0:16:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平时想要写曲子的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.72,0:16:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却总是无法写好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.64,0:16:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是旋律却突然浮现在脑海里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.06,0:16:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  能让我听听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.28,0:17:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚的真的是你写的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.07,0:17:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我应该到哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.95,0:17:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK  我知道那
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.82,0:17:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.28,0:17:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK  到时见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.03,0:18:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我第一次乘直升机
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.18,0:18:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又带这个来给Beck了  拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.72,0:18:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  住口
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.81,0:18:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想开就开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.06,0:18:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为在这里我就不敢开枪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.40,0:18:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.44,0:18:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正在谈生意的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.17,0:18:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我们要飞往哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.67,0:18:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北部
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.93,0:19:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸雄  今天是你喜欢的关东煮喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.88,0:19:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.76,0:19:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道我是谁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.43,0:19:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认识的女人中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.72,0:19:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有一人的声音是像喝醉酒般的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.81,0:19:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.85,0:19:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样你们就可以参演Greatful Sound了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.44,0:20:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷恩大力推荐你们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.94,0:20:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连兰也无法抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.65,0:20:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大婶  这件事我们还没决定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.02,0:20:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.03,0:20:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要跟团员们商量决定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.53,0:20:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都很想去Greatful Sound吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.50,0:20:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚我跟雷恩谈了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.79,0:20:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也到会场逛了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.25,0:20:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.75,0:20:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他出的条件太苛刻了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.25,0:20:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我们能承受的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.39,0:20:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  龙介
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.47,0:20:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.52,0:20:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雄  你也来帮我穿针吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.44,0:20:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.48,0:20:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想让你听一下这个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.70,0:21:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你可以写出这样的曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.93,0:21:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.97,0:21:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.92,0:21:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连接的部分就完全不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.73,0:21:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.50,0:21:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我决定了 小雄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.32,0:21:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.96,0:21:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要参演Greatful Sound
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.42,0:21:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真…真…真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.76,0:21:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…我们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.35,0:22:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DB不出演吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.64,0:22:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想给艾迪添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.94,0:22:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.40,0:22:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  雷恩开出的条件是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.03,0:22:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个我到时再说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.32,0:22:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前是要专注到提升大家的技巧上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.66,0:22:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千叶  你向主办单位拜托他们就会给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.91,0:22:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.71,0:22:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在害羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.17,0:22:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.55,0:22:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得了的夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.72,0:22:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常不得了的夏天将要来临
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.34,0:24:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们终于往北前进了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.22,0:24:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞台就是Greatful Sound
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.10,0:24:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一周  前夜祭
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.76,0:24:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看好咯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
